6192}\n\n## Impact\n\nStored XSS to Account Takeover","weakness":{"id":62,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Stored"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":2016192,"file_name":"recording-1667416640491.webm","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/26g5kkz6fwkxu33fagqdpw5q2pj4?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22recording-1667416640491.webm%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27recording-1667416640491.webm\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fwebm\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ2AOOH4U7%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T073958Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIDXUhfeWK%2F%2FgENm9NZ3vJzC%2BnF6lwiJ4i9gqLUzKwZVFAiEAqNndjHUjMVISdSuaLhwLPjQa%2FIH2LzdMjZcycVtkeSsqugUI8P%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDJRQoaV6SZf5Se5G0iqOBYxfpGtkhbE9QQdD%2FoMEOG2uucVDJUtWQpOhBK8QnOlBv%2F%2B4KMzU8PAz9xxB7%2FEHJCTA7X3G6UWoKUy7o1IT2zkcq1vnXjPW%2Fm77LDp5fxb2KHJX0EDW4mxa4qT7EK74KxZ8Gl8AImj8Yh9PsAL%2FAWp41zi%2Fx0H2w5cP50950crTfSXQsWXhlz0V0YmstfoE5eBurht7Ba%2Bct8SbxKew%2BgPRECgB7ibtWGkcSiRF93TBxoDyqodvARjWaKV2NWHEJi0clK6t6W4I8lwKU1%2B40sW0aCkiM%2Ffs7mMN%2F5E1xxPKGUVJ6Ed%2BCSE6rhceECyJyn1oGApliNJ7TjPNS47gc%2BQc6zotYmQOS3sxvRTS6kKyqRFtWBolm6JuGQwZ8%2BvfrYECrDuYYPbmQCqBC1UWXAkNO9YoDZPkUI5Q1nQC27%2F9fOE28%2FuxzrZcZloFLhimKyCo7SSOcIzngf2Mx%2FMEw6gUIaz8T5tr%2BUcB%2FcnMOcLw8e2QQIDzxfF0iVnEMzarD2r2ia7LES46skuOWR%2BIiV696SgRmdVU1ORUmQ7QBOSg%2BaQwLm4T6gwo1oGmjZFHVDjpNCuPNbKxF4VKunW3mav1pdgizeawjPDWdWEzOAUv88bViGehRs%2FwPeU2X7xUdbR9gIaxGzjcOdiSOib3qxg4pIWRWPlYu5baRR%2FyLObR5KQ9BmSIM03JLHDv%2FxEBchpcyJUegg8wMGsL9SghKCKlbg3ku9r1f9HgFZVZC2xXpVJlIV%2Fo1x1Ny4QcP59gZwcRORFDuig4HUDAoy4kZg20b%2FP0TDZJH7CmWvkNmgLU%2FGjQZMtfq2T3GeWiizjjPgZHYAEbz74mtrOHkg73iJA078v8UmDIvU0A9UDe7TCc1sbPBjqxAZfWVwTln0NxwzBRF7P%2BW6UNvywWEDG2Meis5GPhqVffyO5j6IAOLQurV0pDtRgSuvLnxEBH2nBtlXCG%2BOphnjN6Ucn3ntz18fFTFhO%2BhvJbrThsxKzS5XGOoSahF3eQVSmqOqrEwyKulkSYZGgBoEiYrokeG5WAx5yx7Dk3uRUI4HeUl12C89%2BmDqS%2BlbjkiuhEKXx5ipEWvRZ1x%2F33PK8YbUMZbZf3wMqJo%2B9FHZJ9Ug%3D%3D\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026X-Amz-Signature=a3f0f319fabe39a25e8a9041b5458db63aa907b5772cb063d96519a0866d63a1","file_size":1993835,"type":"video/webm","moderated":null}],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2023-04-01T19:59:48.682Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-97069209.44670147,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":116,"voters":["nicochess","mokusou","p4n7h3rx","8910jq","sufyan0x01","skyw1per","uneefa","loaymorad","orange303","ganeshbagaria","and 106 more..."],"severity":{"rating":"high","score":8.2,"author_type":"User","metrics":{"attack_vector":"network","attack_complexity":"low","privileges_required":"none","user_interaction":"required","scope":"changed","confidentiality":"high","integrity":"low","availability":"none"}},"structured_scope":{"databaseId":194208,"asset_type":"URL","asset_identifier":"www.abritel.fr","max_severity":"critical"},"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"is_exploit_agent_supported?":false,"is_linear_agent_ui_supported?":false,"summaries":[{"category":"team","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false},{"id":266692,"category":"researcher","content":"I was able to Takeover Accounts Via Cache Poisoning (XSS)\n\nThis was possible due to:\n\n1. `hav` cookie was reflected in the Response on https://www.abritel.fr/annonces/location-vacances/france_midi-pyrenees_46_stcere_dt0.php.js\n```javascript\nvar hav=\"value from cookie\"\n```\n\n2. The server had a protection where it was \"Hiding\" double quotes, however the server was not doing that with greater than and less than symbols (\u003c\u003e) which allowed me to closed the script tag and using that double quotes protection I was able to Bypass the WAF easily\n\nWAF would trigger when:\n\n```http\nCookie: hav=xss\"\u003c/script\u003e\u003csvg/onload=alert(document.domain)\u003e\n```\n---\n\nBut using double quotes I was able to bypass the WAF:\n\n```http\nCookie: hav=xss\"\u003c/sc\"ript\u003e\u003csv\"g/onloa\"d=aler\"t\"(document.doma\"in)\u003e\n```\n\nWhich reflected in the response as:\n\n```html\nvar hav=\"xss\u003c/script\u003e\u003csvg/onload=alert(document.domain)\u003e\"\n```\n\n\n3. The Server sees https://www.abritel.fr/annonces/location-vacances/france_midi-pyrenees_46_stcere_dt0.php.js as a \"cacheable\" response, therefore the reflected value in the cookie was saved in that Page, any user who visited https://www.abritel.fr/annonces/location-vacances/france_midi-pyrenees_46_stcere_dt0.php.js would get XSSed\n\n4. Session cookie was HTTPonly Flagged, however, In this same page where the XSS was, there was a JS Variable called `window.INITIAL_STATE.system.cookie`  where the session was located in clear text\n\nWith these four factors combined, I was able to Takeover Accounts\n\nTeam Fixed this by not reflecting ‘hav’ anymore.\n\n\n[X](https://twitter.com/bxmbn)\n","updated_at":"2023-12-12T16:19:51.010Z","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false,"attachments":[],"user":{"id":1320367,"username":"bombon","name":"","bio":"","cleared":true,"verified":true,"website":null,"location":"United States","created_at":"2020-09-13T00:06:25.969Z","url":"https://hackerone.com/bombon","hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false,"user_type":"hacker","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/variants/f3rg2l1asffqs286fqrs8qn1prcm/3cb67cc78dc0cba55b102dd9eca2ee89b206d3e960be830f070583d9070b69ef?response-content-disposition=inline%3B%20filename%3D%22Screenshot_20211123-004623_Twitter.jpg%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screenshot_20211123-004623_Twitter.jpg\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fjpeg\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ2AOOH4U7%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T073958Z\u0026X-Amz-Ex